{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"Misc刷题记录","date":"2023-06-13T18:00:10.496Z","updated":"2023-06-13T18:16:50.454Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Misc刷题记录.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>Misc刷题记录.md</p>\n<h1 id=\"BUgku\"><a href=\"#BUgku\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUgku\"></a>BUgku</h1><h2 id=\"easy-nbt\"><a href=\"#easy-nbt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"easy_nbt\"></a>easy_nbt</h2><p>解压附件后发现</p>\n<p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" data-src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140203664.png\" data-caption=\"image-20230614020105319\"><img src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140203664.png\" alt=\"image-20230614020105319\"></a></p>\n<p>题目名为nbt，搜索nbt，发现是一种存储格式，而后了解到dat文件是一种nbt文件，解压dat文件后搜索flag找到flag</p>\n<p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" data-src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140203598.png\" data-caption=\"image-20230614020213058\"><img src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140203598.png\" alt=\"image-20230614020213058\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"这是一张单纯的图片\"><a href=\"#这是一张单纯的图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"这是一张单纯的图片\"></a>这是一张单纯的图片</h2><p>用010editor打开图片，在底部发现</p>\n<p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" data-src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140207202.png\" data-caption=\"image-20230614020713156\"><img src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140207202.png\" alt=\"image-20230614020713156\"></a></p>\n<p>&amp;#编码，是html编码，改后缀为html，此时再打开</p>\n<p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" data-src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140208781.png\" data-caption=\"image-20230614020803700\"><img src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140208781.png\" alt=\"image-20230614020803700\"></a></p>\n<p>发现flag key{you are right}</p>\n<h2 id=\"隐写\"><a href=\"#隐写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"隐写\"></a>隐写</h2><p>题目名为隐写，下载附件后得到图片</p>\n<p>根据png的格式进行查看，第一行是png的pe头，第二行是png的宽和高，将第二行宽和高修改为相同，就可以了。 （固定）八个字节89 50 4E 47 0D 0A 1A 0A为png的文件头 （固定）四个字节00 00 00 0D 代表数据块的长度为13 （固定）四个字节49 48 44 52（即为ASCII码的IHDR）是文件头数据块的标示（IDCH） （可变）13位数据块（IHDR)</p>\n<p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" data-src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140216652.png\" data-caption=\"image-20230614021604606\"><img src=\"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202306140216652.png\" alt=\"image-20230614021604606\"></a></p>\n","text":"Misc刷题记录.md BUgkueasy_nbt解压附件后发现 题目名为nbt，搜索nbt，发现是一种存储格式，而后了解到dat文件是一种nbt文件，解压dat文件后搜索flag找到flag 这是一张单纯的图片用010editor打开图片，在底部发现 &amp;#编码，是htm...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":405,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#BUgku\"><span class=\"toc-text\">BUgku</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#easy-nbt\"><span class=\"toc-text\">easy_nbt</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%A0%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">这是一张单纯的图片</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%9A%90%E5%86%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">隐写</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"quan9i","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303140010598.jpeg","link":"/","description":"国家一级保护废物","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/quan9i","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/Reme_mber","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"JAVA IO流","uid":"28fab77566c6f0e9ee58d916e868a3c4","slug":"JAVA IO流","date":"2023-05-28T16:51:30.000Z","updated":"2023-06-01T04:51:01.964Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JAVA IO流.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://quan9i.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/202303141527260.png","text":"前言向Drunkbaby师傅